criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  LUTS presence, proven by:

               1. IPSS questionnaire (Score >20);

               2. OR uroflowmetry result (Qmax <10 ml/s);

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Prostate volume > 120 cc

          -  Prostate cancer on pathology;

          -  Urethral strictures;

          -  Bladder calculi;

          -  Prior prostate surgery;

          -  Neurogenic bladder dysfunction.
